moments.headline: Listening to Summer Sunshine by The Corrs

Earlier this morning while I was working in front of my laptop, I heard someone's mumbling a song that I'm really familiar with. Just like a recitation of tune in a high pitch, but without words which can add up into a whole sentence. As the voice get louder and pitch get higher, I came to realize that it came from someone I know. But, could it be.... To confirm my assumption, I asked that person, Me: "Did you just sing a Jigglypuff song???" Him: "I can't wait to play Pokemon in Palembang this weekend!!!!" And so he giggled.
